# Assets Directory

This directory is for visual assets used in GitHub presentation.

## preview.png

Add a social preview image here (1280x640px recommended) for GitHub repository settings.

Suggested content:
- Skill name: "Local Fun Discovery"
- Tagline: "Curated local recommendations through conversation"
- Simple, clean design with a map pin or location icon

To use: Go to repository Settings → General → Social preview → Upload preview.png
